metadata.name: Hot Poppies
metadata.description:
Inspired by Richard Quinn, this is one of the artworks  celebrating Platinum Jubilee of 2022 and the heritage of British fashion designers. It has been created as part of Adriana's collaboration with MSM magazine and Bicester Village. Bold poppies and colours are bridging the empowered lady with her iconic outfit. . 

1/1 Digital, hand drawn, Procreate.
